        },
        {
            "title": "中集安瑞科折讓7.73%配股籌7.8億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中集安瑞科(03899)公布，擬配股集貟7.8億元；配股價9.79元，較該股昨收市價10.61元折讓約7.73%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中集安瑞科官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/03899-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中集安瑞科官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/11/03899-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中集安瑞科官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收市價10.742元計，配股價較之折讓8.86%，較前10個交易日平均收市價10.418元則折讓6.03%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">集資淨額約7.74億元，約50%用於清潔能源業務的資本性支出；其餘約50%用於一般業務運作。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15595771-%e4%b8%ad%e9%9b%86%e5%ae%89%e7%91%9e%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%937-73%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c7-8%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
